title: My Name Isn't On The list
body:
Hi guys, I was just looking at the list for that nautilus wall which has all the people who contributed to the ocean week, and I made like 30+ points and my name isn't on their, but I'm wondering if it's because I haven't gone on league since the end of 
that cause my pc broke but plz hallllp!{{champion:32}}

replies.body:
Hey there,

If you're talking about the [recent ocean week (2016)](http://promo.oce.leagueoflegends.com/en/oceanweek2016/) then your name wouldn't be on the nautilus wall as that was for the 2015 ocean week.
What is the most recent one and when is the wall for that coming out?

Couldn't tell you when that's coming out, here is the event recap for the most recent ocean week.

http://oce.leagueoflegends.com/en/news/community/community-events/oceania-victorious
